* [[Emma Swan]] in ''[[Once Upon a Time (TV series)|Once Upon a Time]]'' was a bail bondsperson in the beginning of the TV series.
* In the TV series ''[[Sneaky Pete]]'', many characters are in the bail bonds business.
* [[Robert Forster]] plays bail bondsman Max Cherry in the [[Quentin Tarantino]] film ''[[Jackie Brown]]''.
* [[Joe Pantoliano]] played bail bondsman Eddie Mascone in 1988's ''[[Midnight Run]]''.

